item.title: About
item.description: I graduated from City College of New York with a Bachelors in Science in Computer Science. I am an avid game developer highly interested in Optimizations and high performance computing Game AI Computer Graphics I’ve built a bunch of small workflow tools within Unity and are opened source on Github. Feel free to take a look at various tools I built here.
